      <section id="contact" style="margin-top:22px;">
        <h2>문의하기</h2>
        <p class="muted">간단한 메시지를 남겨주세요 — 메일로 연결됩니다.</p>

        <form onsubmit="submitContact(event)" class="contact-form" aria-label="Contact form">
          <input class="input" id="name" name="name" placeholder="이름" required />
          <input class="input" id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="이메일" required />
          <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="메시지를 입력하세요..." required></textarea>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center">
            <button class="cta" type="submit">보내기</button>
            <button type="button" class="close-btn" onclick="copyEmail()">이메일 복사</button>
          </div>
          <div id="formNote" class="muted" style="margin-top:8px;font-size:13px">※ 실제 서비스용 메일/백엔드가 필요하면 알려줘. GitHub Pages에선 mailto로 전송합니다.</div>
